==Coaching staff==
* Coach: [[William Ward (American football)|William Ward]]
* Assistant coach: [[William McCauley]]
* Trainer: James Robinson, hired in 1896 from his position with the Manhattan Athletic Club<ref>{{cite news|title=The Football Field|newspaper=Logansport Pharos|date=1896-10-03}}</ref>
* Manager: Ward W. Hughes
* Assistant manager: Charles O. Cook

